-The next cycle should search for a low-turnover regime overlay that keeps the drawdown and funding-aware gains while preserving cost survival. The cost-surviving funding and drawdown filters are weaker on raw net but are useful controls.
+The next cycle should validate the funding threshold and persistence interaction before packaging a participant-strategy asset.
 
